            <fr:title text="Fiber">Fiber</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-001Q.agda" type="external">erct-001Q.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>The <fr:em><fr:strong>fiber</fr:strong></fr:em> of a function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex> at an element <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b:B]]></fr:tex> is the type consisting of elements <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a\colon  A]]></fr:tex> equipped with identifications <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p\colon  fa=b]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:authors>
              <fr:author>
                <fr:link href="foreign-erct-jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="//erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
              </fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2023</fr:year>
              <fr:month>12</fr:month>
              <fr:day>20</fr:day>
            </fr:date>
            <fr:anchor>11716</fr:anchor>
            <fr:addr type="user">//erct/erct-001R</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>foreign-erct-erct-001R.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Path object structure on fibers"><fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0010.xml" title="Path object" addr="//erct/erct-0010" type="local">Path object</fr:link> structure on <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001Q.xml" title="Fiber" addr="//erct/erct-001Q" type="local">fibers</fr:link></fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Example</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-001R.agda" type="external">erct-001R.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>Given <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A\to  B]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b:B]]></fr:tex>, we shall impose a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0010.xml" title="Path object" addr="//erct/erct-0010" type="local">path object</fr:link> structure on the <fr:em><fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001Q.xml" title="Fiber" addr="//erct/erct-001Q" type="local">fiber</fr:link></fr:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}fx=b]]></fr:tex> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b]]></fr:tex>. The family
<fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathord {\vartriangle }
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen f-=b\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\colon  A\to \mathsf {PathObj}]]></fr:tex> given by <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0013.xml" title="The intrinsic path object on a type" addr="//erct/erct-0013" type="local">intrinsic path objects</fr:link> in each component is <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0032.xml" title="Right cleaving of a family of path objects" addr="//erct/erct-0032" type="local">right-cloven</fr:link> over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathord {\vartriangle }A]]></fr:tex>:</fr:p>
            <fr:ol><fr:li>for <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p\colon  x = y]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\phi :fy=b]]></fr:tex>, we define <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p^*b\colon  fx=b]]></fr:tex> to be identification <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {act}_{f}p\cdot  \phi ]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
 <fr:li>the <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0032.xml" title="Right cleaving of a family of path objects" addr="//erct/erct-0032" type="local">unit law</fr:link> can be seen to hold using the unit laws for composition of identification.</fr:li></fr:ol>
            <fr:p>Therefore, we may compute the <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0036.xml" title="Contravariant sum of right-cloven families of path objects" addr="//erct/erct-0036" type="local">contravariant sum</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \int _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathord {\vartriangle }A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \int _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathord {\vartriangle }A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \int _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathord {\vartriangle }A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \int _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathord {\vartriangle }A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\mathord {\vartriangle }
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen fx=b\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}]]></fr:tex> using the cleaving above, with <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,\phi \right \rparen \mathclose {}
 \approx _{\mathchoice {\textstyle \int _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathord {\vartriangle }A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \int _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathord {\vartriangle }A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \int _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathord {\vartriangle }A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \int _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathord {\vartriangle }A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\mathord {\vartriangle }
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen fx=b\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen y,\psi \right \rparen \mathclose {}
]]></fr:tex> definitionally equal to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen p: x= y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen p: x= y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen p: x= y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen p: x= y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}} \phi  = \mathsf {act}_{f}p\cdot  \psi ]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
